{"tid":1440322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[純學術討論] 抗爭者/遊擊隊聖經 - Anarchist Cookbook","createTime":"2019-08-10T11:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T14:42:31.000Z","uid":61589,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0049c0d121f16133d03869cca5418f6f748713","tid":1440322,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:43:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">注 : 此post為純學術討論, 並不鼓吹任何非法行為<br />\n亦同光復香港 時代革命運動絕對無關<br />\n如有雷同, 實屬巧合</span></span><br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1024235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1024235&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=9642f859\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1024235&h=d864fc99\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1024235</a><br />\n下載link<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.preterhuman.net/texts/terrorism_and_pyrotechnics/explosives/MISC/Anarchist%20Cookbook%20-%20William%20Powell.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.preterhuman.net%2Ftexts%2Fterrorism_and_pyrotechnics%2Fexplosives%2FMISC%2FAnarchist%2520Cookbook%2520-%2520William%2520Powell.pdf&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=01b7889b\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.preterhuman.net/texts/terrorism_and_pyrotechnics/explosives/MISC/Anarchist%20Cookbook%20-%20William%20Powell.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n啱啱先醒起自己bookmark仲keep住條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望而家個學術討論仲未太遲<br />\n呢本書曾經係多國禁書<br />\n雖然已經有咁上下歷史, 不過到而家仲喺互聯網上廣為流傳<br />\n雖然只得英文版, 不過D字都唔算深<br />\n內容由簡單既雞尾酒/陷阱製作方法到自製炸藥, 槍械介紹都有.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">導讀 :</span><br />\n心急想睇重點既同學可以skip前言、Chapter 1同Chapter 2<br />\n前言主要係介紹無政府主義(Anarchism). 本書初版係1971年美國, 正值反越戰運動及嬉皮士高峰時期, 有興趣認識歷史同社會學既巴絲可以睇下<br />\nChapter 1係講毒品同迷幻藥等, 同上, 純粹因為嬉皮士文化同毒品有相當淵源, 鍾意Breaking Bad既同學都可以研究下<br />\nChapter 2 係講通訊設備, 包括如何鈎線, 信號干擾等. 但本書寫於七十年代, 當時仲係用緊有線電話同未數碼化既無線電. 所以呢類技巧喺呢個無線年代都相當過時<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點 :</span></span><br />\nChapter 3係介紹武器及各種戰鬥技巧, 包括徒手搏擊(hand to hand)同持刀搏擊有咩注意重點, 攻擊咩部位可以即時制伏敵人甚至致命等<br />\n仲有各種自製利器鈍器等,<span style=\"color: red;\"> 最有趣係一支四吋長既帽針(或者幼鐵枝)竟然可以用黎暗殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要由耳孔插入就可以直達腦部, 一擊斃命</span><br />\n槍械果part都係無乜特別, 一來outdate,二來香港人無乜機會接觸槍械<br />\n不過佢有介紹下自製消音器果D都幾有趣<br />\n最後有講到既包括<span style=\"color: red;\">如何自製催淚氣, 同埋中左催淚氣後既治療<br />\n原來皮膚食左煙之後用食油/BB油抹一次, 再用酒精抹一次, 會比用水更有效</span><br />\n<br />\nChapter 4係各種中伏陷阱同<strong>火魔法介紹</strong>, <span style=\"color: red;\">初階既火魔法有雞尾包, 原來電油同機油用2:1比例整既雞尾包更香更脆</span>. 跟住仲有其他高階火魔法以至大魔導士級魔法<br />\n<br />\n希望大家重拾書本, 快樂學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ccd70479d20a4a0686cb9a63c098bc1a33a68c","tid":1440322,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:03:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"914b8ebee91a28c00f3b9143c7944ec761ee006e","tid":1440322,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"無人想學術討論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24efb4a58745711dbe4309cb6e0712fa64f27c1d","tid":1440322,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"914b8ebee91a28c00f3b9143c7944ec761ee006e","tid":1440322,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"無人想學術討論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:42:31.000Z","msg":"你不如重開，標題直接講重點（如何戰鬥）"}]}